{"tid":1217421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中》「推倒林鄭！推倒惡法！」 民陣16日發動遊行","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:50.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c90b5bd3044cc2153605fa027ad4fbe0004a0cd0","tid":1217421,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"反送中》「推倒林鄭！推倒惡法！」 香港民陣16日發動遊行<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-13<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「反送中」行動發起團體「民間人權陣線」表示，目前已向香港警方提出集會遊行，目前擬定於星期日（16）和星期一（17）舉行。而遊行訴求則包括，特首林鄭月娥下台。<br />\n<br />\n根據「民間人權陣線」臉書以及Telegrm發布的訊息，民間人權陣線呼籲市民參加「推倒林鄭！推倒惡法！」遊行。民陣表示，周日下午兩點半舉行大型遊行，預計從維園遊行是政府總部。另外，下週一則將進行「三罷」總集會。<br />\n民陣指出，此次遊行訴求共3點，包括「譴責警方暴力鎮壓市民」、「撤回逃犯條例修訂」、「林鄭月娥必須下台！」<br />\n<br />\n民陣表示對於警方以「致命武力」開槍表達強烈譴責，並指出，警方在大型集會向市民開槍，是「回歸以來首見」。對於特首林鄭月娥，民陣表示，林鄭無視警方開槍鎮壓，確定性集會為「暴動」，「愧為人母，愧為特首！」<br />\n民陣強調，如果政府拒絕撤回修例，所有建制派議員必須順應主流民意，公開表明會投下反對票。<br />\n<br />\n民陣先前所申請的集會是從今11日早上10點至14日晚間，不過在昨（12）晚，被港府定調為「暴動」，導致今天的集會無法如期舉行。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"6d93c5a642ce37e49cb3e2ae8732134578fc8f59","tid":1217421,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1000/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php5Oy71F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1000%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php5Oy71F.png&h=5b35398e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05134324ec2e46f59bad8d95b69df2541d19902f","tid":1217421,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpv79804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpv79804.jpg&h=1fffa658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpwQcUsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpwQcUsT.jpg&h=8cfa232c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecba904ec6136bc5decd3e06aeb03c60feece598","tid":1217421,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:01:50.000Z","msg":"幾時救番啲義士？"}]}